fact.TriggerEmulation

Class EmulateLogic

  • java.lang.Object
    • fact.TriggerEmulation.EmulateLogic
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    stream.Processor

    public class EmulateLogic
extends Object
implements stream.Processor
    Emulate the n-out-of-4 trigger logic of the trigger unit and the n-out-of-40 logic of the trigger master by applying it to the array of trigger primitives. ï»¿A trigger decision is taken when N out of the 40 primitives * have a rising edge within a time-window adjustable from 8 ns to 68 ns in steps of 4 ns. * Created by jbuss on 26.08.18.
